## Conclusion

The MobileAgent successfully executed the primary sequence: opening Taobao, entering the video section, navigating to the reward center, and claiming a task. However, swipe actions repeatedly failed due to **coordinate out‑of‑bounds** because the model generated relative coordinates > 1000 and the mapping logic lacked boundary clipping.

**Adding the clipping fix above will resolve the swipe issue** and ensure all actions operate within the valid screen area.
